middleware package for @TARGET_TRIPLE@

Components:
- Redis @REDIS_VERSION@: @REDIS_STATUS@
- MinIO @MINIO_REF@
- etcd @ETCD_VERSION@

Toolchain inputs:
- Go @GO_VERSION@ for MinIO and etcd cross builds
- clang/LLVM package image for Redis Linux cross builds

Installed layout:
- bin/redis-server, bin/redis-cli, bin/redis-benchmark on Linux targets
- bin/minio
- bin/etcd, bin/etcdctl, bin/etcdutl
- manifest.env

Redis note:
The MinGW package does not include Redis because upstream Redis server does not
support native Windows builds. MinIO and etcd are included for all five package
targets.
